lead_paragraph: The autopsies relay the chaos in the conference room where the assault occurred and confirm that all of the 14 people who were killed died quickly.

headline.print_headline: Autopsies Show San Bernardino Victims Died Quickly and Reveal Details of Carnage
headline.main: Autopsies of San Bernardino Victims Reveal Details of Carnage

snippet: The autopsies relay the chaos in the conference room where the assault occurred and confirm that all of the 14 people who were killed died quickly.
abstract: San Bernardino County, Calif, releases heavily redacted autopsies of 14 people killed in Dec 2015 terrorist attack, which show victims died quickly but endured chaotic final moments.
